{"tid":1547001,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【太子冇死人】消防處 重申：10變7因爲「重複計算」","createTime":"2019-09-06T13:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T01:13:10.000Z","uid":226548,"like":2,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a2c16c0923a3bbe47be399a896fc7633afb1d8","tid":1547001,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:47:48.000Z","msg":"2019-09-06 HKT 20:44<br />\n<br />\n消防處表示，就網上傳言指處方在8月31日晚上的港鐵太子站事故中，刻意隱瞞實際傷者數目，消防處重申，一直是按現場人員的觀察與紀錄，如實向傳媒提供有關資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1479206_1_20190906211804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1479206_1_20190906211804.jpg&h=45782e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消防處說，有網民因得悉現場<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救護指揮官當晚曾報告有10名傷者，但隨後更正為7名</span></strong>，揣測消防處不恰當地更改資料。處方重申，事發時站內情況混亂，傷者分散不同位置，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">該處人員初步點算時可能有重複計算部份傷者。</span></strong>當救護指揮官安排了7名傷者在月台上接受初步治理、分流及集中於一個地點處理後，沒有其他人士向救護人員表示需要協助。以上情況均會導致初步點算和最後需要處理的傷者數目不同。"},{"pid":"d2e68a1d8bc5bb0284b6daaf35c01e9ff9b1d65b","tid":1547001,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:48:13.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7610891252fccbdcd32e12225e442dff6573a7fe","tid":1547001,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:48:24.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479206-20190906.htm\" data-sr-url=\"htt